    "description": "Cannon Canines is a 3D, minitank-driving, action-adventure game! <br>Play as one of the Cannon Canines, and join a crew of freedom-fighting animals in the Pawpad Isles in order to free your friends from a tyrannical megacorporation.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as an adorable dog! </li><li> Blow up your boss's stuff! </li><li> Build a tank out of garbage!<br> </li><li> Hang out with weirdo rebels! Talk to a panda about coffee!</li></ul><br>Speed through an explosive, bite-sized adventure and unlock new abilities! Pick up the wreckage of your enemies to build and equip new parts. Then, use their own machines to blow up their stuff!<br><br>There's lots of stuff that needs blasting, and you're the one who's going to blast it in Cannon Canines!",
